"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\", \"score\": 0.9917050422145872, \"rank\": 0.008364184207337026, \"text\": \"Republic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All right reserved |Privacy Policy|Terms of use  Gain access to up to 10 free articles per month.\", \"from\": 6653, \"to\": 6750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Already have an account?Log                         in\", \"from\": 6752, \"to\": 6806, \"entities\": []}]}"